                <note rend="inline" type="source">810.79611 Pan American Airways, Inc./57:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Geissler</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-04-18T19:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 18, 1928—7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>36. Department’s 21, March 16, 5 p.m. Pan American Airways report MacGregor
                    having difficulties in his negotiations. Report briefly by cable, fully by mail
                    present situation and render all possible assistance.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
